    <h1>Orphan Repositories</h1>

    <ul class="breadcrumb">
        <li><a href="index.html">Dashboard</a></li>
        <li>Orphans</li>
    </ul>

    <p class="meta">Repositories with no identifiable code owners (CODEOWNERS absent or empty).
        1 orphans out of the assessed repositories in <code>TestOrg</code>.</p>

    
    <div class="table-wrapper">
        <table class="data-table" data-sortable>
            <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th data-sort-type="text"><span class="tooltip-header" tabindex="0" data-tooltip="Repository name; links to it on GitHub when a URL is known.">Repository</span></th>
                    <th data-sort-type="text"><span class="tooltip-header" tabindex="0" data-tooltip="The repository's GitHub visibility: Public, Internal, or Private.">Visibility</span></th>
                    <th data-sort-type="text"><span class="tooltip-header" tabindex="0" data-tooltip="GitHub login of the author of the most recent commit on the default branch; links to their profile when known.">Last Committer</span></th>
                    <th data-sort-type="date"><span class="tooltip-header" tabindex="0" data-tooltip="Date of the most recent commit on the repository's default branch.">Last Commit</span></th>
                    <th data-sort-type="text"><span class="tooltip-header" tabindex="0" data-tooltip="Primary language GitHub detected for the repository, or — when none is set.">Language</span></th>
                    <th data-nosort><span class="tooltip-header" tabindex="0" data-tooltip="Repository description from GitHub, or — when none is set.">Description</span></th>
                </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                
                <tr>
                    <td><a href="https://github.com/TestOrg/active-repo"
                            target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">active-repo</a></td>
                    <td>Public</td>
                    <td>—</td>
                    <td>—</td>
                    <td>—</td>
                    <td class="cell-truncate" title="—">—</td>
                </tr>
                
            </tbody>
        </table>
    </div>
    

    

    


</body>

</html>
